<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">cmd<br />cd &quot;C:\path\to\program\&quot;<br /></div>
<br />
<br />I just put that in a .bat file, click on it, then whatever program I want to use I type in the commands to bring it up.

		

